   Stock prices declined slightly today as traders
cashed in some of the market's recent gains.
   The Dow Jones average of 30 industrials, up 72.40 points last
week, dropped 6.78 to 2,402.68 by 2 p.m. on Wall Street.
   Losers outnumbered gainers by about 5 to 4 in nationwide trading
of New York Stock Exchange-listed issues, with 614 up, 785 down and
499 unchanged.
